+%--- Data Policy --------------------------------------------------------------
+\section*{DATA POLICY}
+
+All data generated in this project --- training logs, reward curves, policy checkpoints,
+demonstration datasets, and safety constraint models --- will be made publicly available
+on GitHub and a persistent data repository under an open-source licence within 30~days
+of corresponding publications.
+The ManiSkill3 simulator is open-source (Apache~2.0).
+No personal, medical, or sensitive data is used; all environments are fully synthetic.
+
